indexes.index_definition: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX contract_items_pkey ON public.contract_items USING btree (id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_auto_renew_end_date ON public.contract_items USING btree (auto_renew, end_date) WHERE (auto_renew = true)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_categoria ON public.contract_items USING btree (categoria)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_churn_date ON public.contract_items USING btree (churn_date) WHERE (churn_date IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_contract_end_date ON public.contract_items USING btree (contract_id, end_date)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_custom_fields ON public.contract_items USING gin (custom_fields)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_holding_id ON public.contract_items USING btree (holding_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_monthly_price ON public.contract_items USING btree (monthly_price) WHERE ((monthly_price IS NOT NULL) AND (is_recurring = true))
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_quote_item_id ON public.contract_items USING btree (quote_item_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_recurring_dates ON public.contract_items USING btree (is_recurring, start_date, end_date) WHERE (is_recurring = true)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_items_related ON public.contract_items USING btree (related_item_id) WHERE (related_item_id IS NOT NULL)

policies.policyname: Users can delete contract items from their holding
policies.qual:
(contract_id IN ( SELECT c.id
   FROM ((contracts c
     JOIN companies comp ON ((c.company_id = comp.id)))
     JOIN user_holdings uh ON ((comp.holding_id = uh.holding_id)))
  WHERE (uh.user_id = auth.uid())))
